sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Activity Unregister Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open unregister URL for activity
    UI->>LW: mount(id)
    LW->>DB: Load activity
    DB-->>LW: Activity record
    LW->>LW: unregister() auto-run

    LW->>DB: Resolve current student profile
    alt No student profile
        DB-->>LW: Student not found
        LW-->>UI: Error toast
    else Student exists
        LW->>DB: Delete activity calendar events
        LW->>DB: Delete activity registration
        alt Success
            DB-->>LW: Rows deleted
            LW-->>UI: Success toast + redirect to details
        else Failure
            DB-->>LW: Exception
            LW-->>UI: Error toast
        end
    end
